---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Overcoming Anxiety in Sex and Relationships — Paula Leech">
  <section class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div class="blob" style="background:var(--color-blush); width:300px; height:300px; top:0; right:0;"></div>
    <div class="text-center relative">
      <img src="/images/img_27.jpg" alt="Overcoming Anxiety in Sex and Relationships book cover" class="max-w-sm mx-auto shadow-2xl" />
    </div>
    <div class="relative">
      <h1>Overcoming Anxiety in Sex and Relationships</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 italic" style="color:var(--color-clay);">"Sex education failed us, leaving gaps we've struggled to fill — often alone. But information can heal."</p>
      <p class="text-xs mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest">— Paula Leech, LMFT CST CSTS</p>

      <p class="mt-8">Learn how anxiety, stress, and pressure affect pleasure, connection, and sexual functioning. This book explores how anxiety shapes our physiology, understanding of ourselves, and our interactions with the world.</p>
      <p class="mt-4">Paula guides readers to identify key sources of anxiety — from family and culture to relationship dynamics and sexual trauma. Offering practical tips and techniques, she encourages readers to rethink their definitions of sex, sexuality, and intimacy. Through mindfulness and embodiment exercises, she provides tools to release tension, work through sexual struggles, and reconnect with the body.</p>
      <p class="mt-4">Accessible and comprehensive, this guide is ideal for sex therapists and anyone facing anxiety-related challenges with themselves and/or their partners.</p>

      <!-- TODO: replace with real Amazon URL -->
      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn mt-8">Buy on Amazon</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
